{"tid":375161,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[圍爐]點解識親技術野就一定比人當係免費奴工?","createTime":"2017-08-26T10:22:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T08:11:35.000Z","uid":60538,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c383fa57bc44f66c1eb58f7f3b3e23b658b3dd8d","tid":375161,"uid":60538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T10:22:31.000Z","msg":"例如識手工藝, 整圖既野, 就一定老奉搵你整野<br />\n出返材料錢或者一百幾十已經皇恩浩蕩<br />\n態度唔好個堆仲要你快或者嫌三嫌四<br />\n<br />\n識整水電或者電腦野<br />\n又會叫你順手整下<br />\n仲話返你轉頭「好簡單之嘛」<br />\n<br />\n識做會計野或者幾句英文仲大獲<br />\n老奉叫你幫手做呢類野<br />\n<br />\n識睇相或者八字算命<br />\n又會有身邊人周不時搵你&quot;睇睇&quot;<br />\n大佬請食餐飯再睇條氣都順啲啦<br />\n<br />\n呢個世界係咪咁多大種乞兒<br />\n利申: 人越大，就算識幾多野都盡量唔講比人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://livequotes.online/library/quotes/spiderman-quotes-with-great-power-comes-great-responsibility/spiderman-quotes-with-great-power-comes-great-responsibility-08.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flivequotes.online%2Flibrary%2Fquotes%2Fspiderman-quotes-with-great-power-comes-great-responsibility%2Fspiderman-quotes-with-great-power-comes-great-responsibility-08.jpg&d=u%2FisQfE7dO%2Ff33Jj%2BdeHbr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=7bcba9a5\" target=\"_blank\">http://livequotes.online/library/quotes/spiderman-quotes-with-great-power-comes-great-responsibility/spiderman-quotes-with-great-power-comes-great-responsibility-08.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"e144ca8f0e5a7f82808be242bb1c5d88de5d7571","tid":375161,"uid":60538,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T10:22:52.000Z","msg":"唔通真係<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://livequotes.online/library/quotes/spiderman-quotes-with-great-power-comes-great-responsibility/spiderman-quotes-with-great-power-comes-great-responsibility-08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flivequotes.online%2Flibrary%2Fquotes%2Fspiderman-quotes-with-great-power-comes-great-responsibility%2Fspiderman-quotes-with-gr